    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Phylum of approximately 50 species of small, ciliated, multicellular animals that are parasitic in marine invertebrates.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
